Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.64,0:00:07.00,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to live in a world of peace\Nwithout conflict, like the one I dreamed of.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.88,0:00:19.80,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't be patient any longer\NThere are things I must say
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.84,0:00:23.08,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,At the evening bus stop\Non the way home
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.08,0:00:25.60,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I Wave to those sunken shoulders,\NBye Bye Bye
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.60,0:00:31.80,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Got to show your Fighting Pose, Oh! Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.84,0:00:37.92,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That world I dreamed of\NIs peaceful every day, without any conflict.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.92,0:00:40.40,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,But in reality,\Nthere are troubles every day
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.40,0:00:44.28,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,And sometimes I regret,\Nthese Rolling days
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.48,0:00:55.00,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Lies probably have little meaning
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.36,0:01:02.12,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,~All my loving\NOtherwise, how can I go on?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.12,0:01:08.92,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,A Sweet Love I dreamed of\Nwhere lovers search for a hideaway
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.92,0:01:11.84,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,But in reality,\Nthe days we can't meet
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.84,0:01:19.12,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Go on; but we still believe,\Nthese Rolling days
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.12,0:01:25.68,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,We may stumble, but Way to go!!\NYeah!! Yeah!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.68,0:01:27.84,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,A mud-caked Rolling star!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.56,0:01:33.37,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,PROTECTION
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.93,0:01:35.05,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Mr. Hollow...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.73,0:01:39.29,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, but Ichigo is out right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.97,0:01:43.61,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,PROTECTION
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.61,0:01:45.13,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... sorry about that...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.89,0:01:52.93,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I still haven't introduced myself.\NI'm Isshin...Kurosaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.13,0:02:07.17,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Remember this...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.93,0:02:12.21,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't tell how strong your opponent is\Nby the size of his zanpakuto...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.77,0:02:28.25,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Only then can you talk to me\Nabout Soul Reapers, boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.13,0:02:38.89,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I-Impossible...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.49,0:02:58.25,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,With just...o-one strike...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.97,0:03:00.97,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.69,0:03:04.29,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Were we saved?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.01,0:03:06.01,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.45,0:03:07.89,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,This is crazy...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.37,0:03:10.25,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,He's incredibly strong...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.21,0:03:13.05,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Is he really Ichigo's...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.81,0:03:16.57,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,- ...stupid father?\N- Yeah! Yeah! Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.61,0:03:17.61,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yahoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.89,0:03:21.01,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you get it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.05,0:03:26.05,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Your revenge...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.93,0:03:28.13,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You came...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.97,0:03:34.97,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Urahara.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.69,0:03:41.09,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a while, Mr. Isshin.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.97,0:03:44.97,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... It looks like your skills\Nhaven't faded.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.98,0:03:46.30,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm relieved.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.65,0:03:50.01,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this? That's a pretty normal thing\Nfor you to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.77,0:03:51.89,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.37,0:03:54.21,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I would hate it if you blamed me
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.25,0:03:56.57,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,if your Spiritual Pressure\Nhad withered away.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.77,0:03:59.17,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I see... Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.41,0:04:02.61,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't blame you if it had faded
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.65,0:04:05.49,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,along with my skills.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.81,0:04:10.53,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,How is it, being a Soul Reaper\Nfor the first time in 20 years?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.61,0:04:12.73,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Not bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.61,0:04:16.65,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you...feel better?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.89,0:04:20.97,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Not bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.01,0:04:25.81,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I never hated that Hollow\Nto begin with.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.97,0:04:33.09,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,If there was something\NI've hated for over 20 years...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.93,0:04:40.69,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It would be my weakness that night\Nwhen I couldn't save Masaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.85,0:04:46.93,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That part of you never changes...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.97,0:04:48.73,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You're just like your son.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.73,0:04:51.05,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not like him!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.09,0:04:52.65,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You are!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.77,0:04:55.13,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I say I'm not!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.37,0:04:57.61,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll leave it at that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.73,0:05:02.25,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Speaking of your son,\Nhave you noticed?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.61,0:05:04.21,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.57,0:05:10.21,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,As you've predicted...\Nthey've made contact.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.13,0:05:17.45,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,The Masked Army. The Visored.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.37,0:05:19.45,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,The Visored?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.93,0:05:21.57,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.57,0:05:25.33,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,They called them\Nthe Masked Army.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.97,0:05:34.53,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,THE MASKED ARMY\NVISORED
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.57,0:05:37.73,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,They're an outlaw group of\Nformer Soul Reapers
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.77,0:05:41.65,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,who tried to gain Hollow powers\Nby using forbidden techniques.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.85,0:05:45.65,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Their whereabouts and\Naims are unknown.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.09,0:05:47.69,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,This is troublesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.85,0:05:51.01,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,The only thing that I do know is that
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.05,0:05:55.37,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,the Visored and the Arrancar\Nare not teamed with each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.01,0:05:59.73,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,But they're not our allies...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.45,0:06:03.61,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,The Visored hate Soul Reapers\Nas well...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.49,0:06:05.49,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.09,0:06:09.69,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,But they made contact\Nwith your son.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.93,0:06:10.93,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That must mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.37,0:06:16.21,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... They're preparing for\Nsome sort of battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.01,0:06:18.61,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.57,0:06:24.93,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,They have probably noticed\Nthe sudden change in the Arrancar.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.73,0:06:30.05,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,So that Hollow really had\Nits mask removed...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.97,0:06:31.97,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,A broken mask...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.29,0:06:34.49,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,An Arrancar.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.65,0:06:36.73,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,BROKEN MASK\NARRANCAR
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.77,0:06:39.57,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,So now they're going to\Nread this as Arrancar?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.93,0:06:44.53,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Until now, we've detected\Nthe naturally occurring Arrancar
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.57,0:06:46.45,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,from time to time...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.33,0:06:52.09,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,But compared to the mock Arrancar\Nwe've confirmed up until now,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.10,0:06:54.60,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,this one's level of perfection was\Nlike nothing we've ever seen before.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.73,0:07:00.57,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Mock Arrancar didn't change\Nfor decades,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.61,0:07:02.29,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,but they suddenly jumped a level.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.53,0:07:05.01,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all so sudden...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.81,0:07:08.89,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You understand what this means, right?\NThis means...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.61,0:07:13.29,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Sosuke Aizen...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.37,0:07:17.85,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,He made contact with\Nthe mock Arrancar
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.89,0:07:22.09,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,and is trying to create a true Arrancar...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.09,0:07:25.25,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,...using the Hogyoku's power.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.17,0:07:29.05,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,According to my calculations,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.09,0:07:33.13,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,the Hogyoku was supposed to\Ntake another year to mature.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.93,0:07:36.97,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, that power isn't complete...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.09,0:07:40.81,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That Arrancar was still incomplete.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.65,0:07:44.89,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,He has jumped a level,\Nbut his Spiritual Pressure was impure.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.49,0:07:49.53,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,He was probably a test subject\Nto gather information
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.57,0:07:52.45,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,on how well he could fight\Nat this level.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.49,0:07:59.41,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,They're at this level now,\Nbut the Hogyoku's power is immense.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.01,0:08:02.49,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Aizen will probably be\Npushing his research
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.53,0:08:04.49,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,so that they can be used in battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.85,0:08:11.05,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,He'll lead those completed "true" Arrancar\Nand a Menos army...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.17,0:08:14.05,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,And come to crush the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.45,0:08:22.49,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.33,0:08:24.93,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do what we can.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.81,0:08:27.33,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever the case,\Nthis is the situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.25,0:08:31.53,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Enemy or ally,\Nwe're all going to make a move.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.37,0:08:33.61,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,The Visored...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.05,0:08:36.93,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Us...and...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.85,0:08:39.21,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Soul Society...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.45,0:08:44.41,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... Someone's coming\Nin this direction.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.69,0:08:47.05,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,This Spiritual Pressure...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.01,0:08:49.49,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It's your son.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.05,0:08:54.61,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be troublesome\Nto see him...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.85,0:08:58.33,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, everyone.\NLet's all go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.57,0:09:00.29,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,- O-Okay.\N- O-Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.57,0:09:07.57,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.69,0:09:10.97,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,All right. I'll be there immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.53,0:09:31.09,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Tsk! What a pain...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.65,0:09:40.53,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you all for coming at\Nsuch short notice!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.05,0:09:45.45,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,We shall now commence\Nthe Captains' meeting!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.65,0:09:54.61,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,KARAKURA FIRST HIGH SCHOOL
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.89,0:10:03.05,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that Spiritual Pressure?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.65,0:10:10.09,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no trace of anyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.37,0:10:15.33,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! This is all because of Hirako...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.65,0:10:18.61,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a Visored.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.25,0:10:22.93,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the same as me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.93,0:10:30.25,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Come with us...Ichigo.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.97,0:10:34.37,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't be on that side.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.93,0:10:44.93,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want me to restore your powers...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.97,0:10:48.81,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Swear to me that\Nyou will not involve yourself
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.85,0:10:50.69,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,with Soul Reapers from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.25,0:10:53.25,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Swear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.05,0:11:04.73,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, Kurosaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.05,0:11:08.09,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, Ichigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.09,0:11:11.85,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Hirako...he came to school\Nas if nothing happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.93,0:11:13.21,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.49,0:11:15.13,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm... Hirako?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.29,0:11:17.73,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah! You remembered my name!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.13,0:11:20.09,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, Orihime!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.13,0:11:23.69,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.77,0:11:26.17,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it? How noisy...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.69,0:11:28.21,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.73,0:11:29.93,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Who am I?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.05,0:11:31.05,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with that,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.09,0:11:34.17,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,"I've been here longer than you"\Nsort of attitude?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.21,0:11:37.25,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I've been here way, way longer!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.53,0:11:39.29,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You've already been hurt...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.53,0:11:41.25,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, let her go!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.29,0:11:43.33,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Inoue doesn't like it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.57,0:11:44.57,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you stupid?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.69,0:11:48.13,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,If she didn't like it she would\Nhave screamed or hit me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.01,0:11:51.69,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,She hasn't done anything.\NThat means that she doesn't mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.73,0:11:53.33,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Orihime?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.69,0:11:55.97,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,W-What's with that\Narrogant attitude?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.01,0:11:57.97,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one who's doing\Nsomething bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.53,0:12:02.53,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I-Isn't that right?!\NI'm not wrong...am I?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.33,0:12:07.05,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It's all right. You're not wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.01,0:12:11.21,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Leave him to me, Keigo.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.65,0:12:13.29,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Ch-Chizuru!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.33,0:12:16.45,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Orihime is a nice girl who\Nwon't make a face
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.49,0:12:19.01,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,even if you do\Nsomething bad to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.10,0:12:22.65,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,So an idiot like you clinging on\Nto her without realizing that
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.69,0:12:25.41,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,has no reason to live in this world!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.09,0:12:29.93,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm...It's a bit strange to be\Nsaying this to an ally...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.97,0:12:34.13,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,but by that logic,\Nyou should be the first one to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.21,0:12:35.61,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Justice in my hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.65,0:12:38.73,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Death to swine! Special attack,\NChizuru Genocide!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.01,0:12:41.57,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to kill him...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.37,0:12:50.77,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Come here for a second, Hirako.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.69,0:12:55.29,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.65,0:12:57.61,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with Ichigo?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.25,0:13:00.01,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Snapping like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.05,0:13:01.85,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Since when was he\Nthe hot-blooded type?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.89,0:13:03.33,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I-Ichigo?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.98,0:13:14.81,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.87,0:13:17.99,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That hurts... What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.43,0:13:20.63,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't need to get so mad...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.15,0:13:24.47,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not as if Orihime\Nis your girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.79,0:13:27.35,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, there's no way\Nthat someone like you
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.39,0:13:29.67,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,could get anywhere with\Na beauty like her.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.19,0:13:31.19,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.87,0:13:34.95,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, apologize to Inoue afterwards!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.35,0:13:36.47,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You should do that!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.43,0:13:42.11,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Like I just said, there's no reason\Nfor you to tell me that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.27,0:13:44.39,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Hirako...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.99,0:13:46.83,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you still coming\Nto this school?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.35,0:13:49.03,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be unreasonable.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.23,0:13:52.23,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a student's duty to go to school.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.95,0:13:57.19,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you come to our school\Nto recruit me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.51,0:14:00.67,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case, you don't have\Nany business here anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.11,0:14:03.27,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.79,0:14:08.59,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you really think that
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.63,0:14:11.47,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd give up so easily?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.11,0:14:20.31,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm persistent...\NI'll hang around you until you say yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.07,0:14:23.19,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It's too late...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.11,0:14:27.91,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Once you become a Visored,\Nyou can't go back.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.91,0:14:33.95,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever you may think,\Nyou're already on our side, Ichigo.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.67,0:14:42.07,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Orihime...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.91,0:14:43.91,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,The big guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.95,0:14:45.95,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Four-eyes...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.99,0:14:49.79,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You think of them all as your friends,\Ndon't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.03,0:14:55.43,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,They're not...\NThey're only your friends for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.11,0:15:00.63,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,If you continue to be a Soul Reaper\Nas you have been, sooner or later...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.51,0:15:04.23,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Your inner Hollow'll swallow you up.\NYou'll lose your sanity...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.23,0:15:10.07,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It's over if that happens.\NYour power will destroy everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.83,0:15:15.67,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Your friends...and your future...\NEverything will get pulled in and crushed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.07,0:15:20.03,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You've already realized that, haven't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.07,0:15:27.07,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Your inner Hollow has become so large\Nthat you can't handle it anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.07,0:15:30.63,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Come with me, Ichigo.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.83,0:15:34.55,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll teach you how to maintain\Nyour sanity.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.43,0:15:43.91,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.99,0:15:47.27,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Want to go into town on\Nthe way home?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.55,0:15:48.63,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.95,0:15:50.99,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to go home by myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.39,0:15:52.99,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.75,0:15:57.59,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,M-Mizuiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.95,0:15:59.55,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,There's something wrong with Ichigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.59,0:16:02.47,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Really? He gets like that sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.71,0:16:06.19,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that's true, but that's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.35,0:16:10.15,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Ichigo is more...\NIt's difficult to put into words, but...umm...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.59,0:16:12.67,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You're just imagining it, Mr. Asano.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.27,0:16:15.07,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Woah! You're suddenly speaking\Nto me politely?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.35,0:16:18.11,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?! Is something wrong, Mr. Asano?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.11,0:16:20.35,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Whoa. Again?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.63,0:16:24.23,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is everyone distancing themselves\Nfrom me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.55,0:16:27.27,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I hate you all!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.95,0:16:33.51,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,How tiring!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.87,0:16:36.83,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I shouldn't do things\NI'm not used to doing...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.03,0:16:39.99,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What was that post-break test?\NHow stupid...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.95,0:16:45.03,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, why do I have to go to\NIchigo's school to recruit him!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.71,0:16:47.39,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I still don't like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.79,0:16:55.47,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That hurts...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.95,0:16:57.03,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Who did that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.35,0:16:58.15,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.11,0:17:05.11,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hiyori!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.23,0:17:12.55,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What's taking you so long,\Nyou spineless worm?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.07,0:17:14.07,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.11,0:17:16.55,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Where is Ichigo Kurosaki?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.87,0:17:18.15,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Um... Not yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.16,0:17:20.39,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Not yet?! What's the meaning of this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.99,0:17:24.55,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Just talk to him and bring him to us!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.99,0:17:28.87,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I told him, but he wouldn't listen!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.91,0:17:31.59,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Then bring him to us by force!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.67,0:17:35.63,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! That's not what\Nyou told me the last time!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.79,0:17:36.79,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I found you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.11,0:17:42.43,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Orihime!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.83,0:17:43.43,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Shinji.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.23,0:17:49.59,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is someone following you, baldy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.27,0:17:56.83,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if we asked Kurosaki\Nhe'd probably say that it was nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.47,0:18:00.63,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,So I came to ask you in person...\NHirako...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.51,0:18:06.99,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?\NWhat do you want with Kurosaki?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.11,0:18:13.15,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you think that we'd tell you\Nif you just asked?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.59,0:18:24.15,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Hiyori Sarugaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.43,0:18:25.03,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.11,0:18:31.79,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Not, "Huh". It's my name!\NTell me your names!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.11,0:18:34.83,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Orihime Inoue...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.23,0:18:36.99,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yasutora Sado.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.03,0:18:42.23,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,A "princess" and a "tiger", huh?\NThose are pretty impressive names!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.95,0:18:44.99,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,We're a "monkey" and "flat"!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.59,0:18:47.63,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I'm so jealous!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.55,0:18:52.43,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What's "flat"?\NI'm the only one that's not a living thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.11,0:18:54.79,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make such\Nforced comparisons, stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.47,0:19:02.03,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,And she's got big breasts\Nand smooth hair!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.19,0:19:05.07,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,She's really annoying!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.55,0:19:06.99,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You're just jealous.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.67,0:19:10.43,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Plus you're only holding\Nthose things against Orihime.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.23,0:19:13.39,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.59,0:19:17.03,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, I have nothing to tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.51,0:19:20.87,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to die here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.03,0:19:25.55,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm very sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.43,0:19:28.43,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.63,0:19:29.91,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't, Inoue!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.35,0:19:32.35,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Sado...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.95,0:19:33.95,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.87,0:19:38.03,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't catch up to them\Nwith our power.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.51,0:19:42.15,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, even if we could...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.27,0:19:45.95,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,We would be killed...for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.07,0:19:49.35,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Shinji, hey, let me go, baldy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.43,0:19:50.91,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to slap them around!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.99,0:19:52.51,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't. Are you stupid?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.71,0:19:54.39,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,We're after Ichigo!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.67,0:19:56.99,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,No need to cause trouble\Nwith others just yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.03,0:19:59.71,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! Let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.75,0:20:01.15,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't give me an enema.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.51,0:20:03.55,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I said... "Stop"!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.15,0:20:05.11,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, baldy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.43,0:20:08.03,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you going to do\Nif I can't get married?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.35,0:20:10.19,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! It's punishment!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.07,0:20:14.35,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It's punishment\Nfor a kid who won't listen!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.55,0:20:15.55,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.67,0:20:19.59,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I said, "stop"!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.87,0:20:25.87,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I hate humans...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.79,0:20:28.87,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.75,0:20:33.43,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I also hate Soul Reapers...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.87,0:20:35.91,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.39,0:20:47.47,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm telling you to wait\Na little longer, stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.71,0:20:55.31,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,DIRECTOR'S OFFICE
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.47,0:21:03.47,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You've come.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.11,0:21:11.31,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me your answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.03,0:21:17.43,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to restore my powers...\Nmy Quincy powers!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.99,0:21:23.83,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to borrow power...\NI want my own power...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.99,0:21:25.99,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,And?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.11,0:21:33.35,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I swear... That I will never again...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.47,0:21:38.11,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,involve myself with Soul Reapers\Nand their associates.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.10,0:22:07.50,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,I met you at age 16
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.54,0:22:13.18,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,and we had\Nan eternal love
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.22,0:22:18.70,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Beneath\Ncherry blossoms petals
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.74,0:22:24.06,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,gently fluttering downward
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.10,0:22:29.54,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That steep and sunny hill
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.58,0:22:35.18,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,where I ran up to see you,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.22,0:22:40.10,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,...And our shadows at\Nthe corner of the park,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.14,0:22:46.50,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,they are still unchanged\Neven today
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.54,0:22:52.34,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You, me,\Nand cherry blossom days,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.38,0:22:57.54,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,we dance\Nand sway in the wind
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.58,0:23:03.18,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Holding in our heart\Nthe unseen future,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.22,0:23:11.10,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,we look up at the pink sky
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.53,0:23:21.72,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,This and this and this...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.72,0:23:22.74,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing, Rin?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.74,0:23:25.81,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Akon, I was asked by the Lieutenant\Nto prepare substitute soul candy.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.81,0:23:27.05,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Is someone going to\Nthe World of the Living?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.05,0:23:28.84,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,The people on this list.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.84,0:23:30.63,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll get pretty noisy there.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.63,0:23:32.38,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Are they that noisy?\Nho's going?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.38,0:23:33.09,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's going? Who's going?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.09,0:23:34.01,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.01,0:23:35.06,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.06,0:23:37.97,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,- Illustrated Guide to Soul Reapers!\N- Mornings have sure been rough lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.97,0:23:40.23,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,- Are you all right, Abarai?\N- Good morning, Lieutenant Hisagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.23,0:23:41.40,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.65,0:23:44.32,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That was a squad member\Nfrom Squad 7, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.32,0:23:47.99,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... We became friends during\Nthe Bount incident.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.99,0:23:52.59,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah...\NIba is strangely conscious of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.59,0:23:53.59,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,He said something like,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.59,0:23:56.46,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,"Squad members don't respect me\Nas much as they used to."
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.46,0:23:58.68,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,He doesn't need to be worried\Nabout that...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.68,0:24:02.01,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,It's hard to believe that people\Nused to respect him.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.01,0:24:03.98,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a pretty cruel thing to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.98,0:24:05.09,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,You spineless worm!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.09,0:24:07.09,B2,,0000,0000,0000,,